            "title": "京東擬發人民幣計價優先票據",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">京東(09618)今早發公告，表示擬於美國境外以離岸交易方式，向非美國投資者發行以人民幣計值的優先無擔保票據。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">發行金額、利率與期限等詳細條款，尚有待落實。京東表示，擬將今次發行集資所得用於一般公司用途，包括償還若干現有債務及支付利息。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15816108-%e4%ba%ac%e6%9d%b1%e6%93%ac%e7%99%bc%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%b9%a3%e8%a8%88%e5%83%b9%e5%84%aa%e5%85%88%e7%a5%a8%e6%93%9a",
